entries.text: See all upcoming schedules for athletic events, some real-time scoring, rosters, and athletic news.

Find your seat, the closest restroom, and the nearest concession stand at State Farm Center. See realtime availability of parking spaces available for purchase and get directions to the entrance of those parking lots around State Farm Center.
Your location may be known at any given time, but never stored.
Easily follow your favorite sports teams with real time score updates, rosters of players and coaches, and the latest athletic news.
We may remember your location over time and store personal preferences.

Buy tickets for athletic events (requires Paciolan login). Make future ordering easy by storing your payment information. Receive notifications of event start and final scores for your favorite teams.
We may securely store your credit card information, remember items you have ordered, and send various notifications to your phone.
We will access your previous orders.

entries.text: Buy Illini Cash for yourself or someone you know.
We will use, but not store, your credit card information.
Check your Illini Cash and Meal Plan balances and see past transactions. Display your Illini ID and MTD bus pass.

We may store your credit card information and phone number and send notifications to your phone. We will store personally identifiable information if you signin with your NetID or a verfied phone number.

entries.text: Show campus dining locations and see menus for up to two weeks in the future.
Show Event and Dining locations near your current location.
Your location may be known at any given time, but never stored.
Store your dining location preferences (including food allergies) and see menus for up to two weeks in the future.

Provide assistance in registering to vote, voting by mail and finding voting locations on election day. Allow you to create a quick poll and receive results from people nearby or far away. Receive notifications that might interest you based on your preferences or location.

We may store your credit card information and phone number and send notifications to your phone. We may store the polls you participate in and start. We may store if you are registered to vote or are signed up for vote by mail.
See events, dining locations and news articles that interest you.

description.text: You may not be able to use all features, but you are anonymous and we don't ask for anything or store any data. Anonymous data will be collected and used to optimize app performance.
See what's happening around you. We use Wifi and Bluetooth location services to improve your experience, but we never store that data.
You can personalize and customize the app. Wifi and Bluetooth location data is stored over time to make recommendations and improve your overall app experience.

Let the app work for you. 
You can access your iCard, save credit cards to make future purchases easier, access health information, and get notifications based on your specific interests.
Access all features, get connected to campus, and let the app suggest tailored experiences that you and your friends all enjoy.
